lemma cond_action_oks_shr_change: "cond_action_oks (ls, (ts, m), ws, is) t cts \<Longrightarrow> cond_action_oks (ls, (ts, m'), ws, is) t cts"
proof(induct cts arbitrary: ls ts m)
case Nil
thus?case
by simp
next
case (Cons ca cts)
thus?case
apply(cases ca)
apply auto
done
qed
